Doesn't sound likely to result in the application getting approved.
They use the info to run a credit check.  Unless you've built up a
credit history under the false SSN and so forth, the credit check will
probably come back negative.  Of course, if it doesn't, and you get
the account and pay the bills on time, you are on your way to building
such a credit history.
